### 心事盒APP API 测试脚本
### 使用方法：安装 VS Code REST Client 插件，点击 "Send Request"

### 1. 发送短信验证码
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/send-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 2. 手机号登录（验证码从后端控制台查看，mock模式为6位随机数）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login-phone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "code": "123456"
}

### 3. 获取个人资料（需要替换为实际返回的token）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

### 4. 发布公开笔记
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

{
  "title": "我的第一篇笔记",
  "content": "这是一篇公开笔记，所有人都可以看到。",
  "visibility": "public",
  "price": 0
}

### 5. 发布付费笔记
POST http://localhost:3000/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

{
  "title": "付费笔记 - 独家内容",
  "content": "这是一篇付费笔记，需要购买才能查看全文。",
  "visibility": "paid",
  "price": 100
}

### 6. 获取笔记列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notes?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

### 7. 获取笔记详情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/notes/替换为实际笔记ID
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

### 8. 购买笔记
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pay/purchase-note
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

{
  "noteId": "替换为实际笔记ID",
  "amount": 100
}

### 9. 申请提现
POST http://localhost:3000/api/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...

{
  "amount": 100,
  "accountName": "张三",
  "accountNumber": "6222021234567890123"
}

### 10. 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 11. 获取统计数据
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer 替换为管理员token

### 12. 获取用户列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer 替换为管理员token

### 13. 获取提现审核列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/withdrawals?page=1&limit=20&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer 替换为管理员token

### 14. 审核提现通过
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/withdrawals/替换为提现ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 替换为管理员token

{
  "status": "approved",
  "remark": "审核通过"
}
